commit.message:
Added light sensor

Added a light sensor that will output the the sensor value on the serial bus.
added gitignore for Leap SDK files

Initial Commit of Arduino Code

Arduino code that reads in commands from the serial port and uses that to control the movement of the robot. Also capable of sending signals if it encounters an obstacle, waiting for user takeover.
integrated solace pubsub+ to leapmotion service
